00:00:06.206 --> 00:00:09.076 position:5% line:83% align:start
[Dio] Do you believe in gravity
between individuals?

00:00:09.109 --> 00:00:10.377 position:16% line:89% align:start
Do you believe that fate

00:00:10.410 --> 00:00:12.580 position:35% line:83% align:start
brought us
together for a reason?

00:00:12.614 --> 00:00:15.282 position:19% line:83% align:start
[young Father Pucchi]
Why, in God's name? Why?

00:00:15.315 --> 00:00:17.919 position:27% line:83% align:start
Why did it have
to end like this?

00:00:17.952 --> 00:00:21.488 position:7% line:83% align:start
[young Weather] Why? Why can't
I just die and be with Perla?

00:00:21.523 --> 00:00:22.055 position:16% line:89% align:start
[young Weather groaning]

00:00:22.690 --> 00:00:25.693 position:35% line:89% align:start
[screams]

00:00:26.794 --> 00:00:29.162 position:16% line:89% align:start
My fury isn't satisfied.

00:00:29.196 --> 00:00:31.131 position:24% line:83% align:start
I'll make you pay
right here and now.

00:00:31.164 --> 00:00:33.601 position:24% line:83% align:start
Weather, I'm going
to eliminate you!

00:00:34.401 --> 00:00:35.302 position:35% line:89% align:start
[gurgles]

00:00:35.335 --> 00:00:36.169 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:00:38.673 --> 00:00:40.508 position:21% line:89% align:start
[suspenseful music]

00:00:40.542 --> 00:00:42.577 position:13% line:83% align:start
[Father Pucchi] And those
without any memories left

00:00:42.610 --> 00:00:44.111 position:21% line:89% align:start
are as good as dead.

00:00:45.680 --> 00:00:48.048 position:30% line:89% align:start
[theme music]

00:02:18.539 --> 00:02:20.675 position:10% line:83% align:start
-[distant car tires screech]
-[snail slime sloshes]

00:02:20.708 --> 00:02:21.976 position:21% line:89% align:start
[Ermes] You dumbass!

00:02:22.010 --> 00:02:23.578 position:30% line:83% align:start
Don't you know
how to drive properly?

00:02:23.611 --> 00:02:25.513 position:10% line:83% align:start
You'd better not be driving
like this on purpose.

00:02:25.546 --> 00:02:28.148 position:16% line:83% align:start
Yeah, right! Like I have
a composure to mess around.

00:02:28.181 --> 00:02:31.218 position:19% line:83% align:start
Just look. These bugs
are eating me alive too!

00:02:32.954 --> 00:02:33.821 position:21% line:89% align:start
[Jolyne] Weather...

00:02:33.855 --> 00:02:34.989 position:33% line:89% align:start
[both] Huh?

00:02:35.023 --> 00:02:36.891 position:30% line:83% align:start
I sense Pucchi
in that direction,

00:02:36.924 --> 00:02:38.291 position:13% line:89% align:start
and Weather is there too.

00:02:39.093 --> 00:02:40.928 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[gasps]
-Are they together?

00:02:40.962 --> 00:02:42.897 position:27% line:83% align:start
I can't say that
with all certainty,

00:02:42.930 --> 00:02:44.498 position:16% line:83% align:start
but I know they're near
each other.

00:02:47.101 --> 00:02:48.168 position:21% line:89% align:start
[Anastasia] Weather!

00:02:48.201 --> 00:02:50.138 position:21% line:83% align:start
What the actual hell
did you just say?

00:02:50.170 --> 00:02:51.906 position:16% line:89% align:start
You want me to kill you?

00:02:51.939 --> 00:02:53.875 position:41% line:83% align:start
-I do.
-Cut the bullshit!

00:02:53.908 --> 00:02:55.143 position:13% line:89% align:start
What do you mean by that?

00:02:55.175 --> 00:02:57.277 position:13% line:89% align:start
What's going on with you?

00:02:57.310 --> 00:02:59.947 position:13% line:83% align:start
I remember this happening
around me once before,

00:02:59.981 --> 00:03:02.016 position:16% line:89% align:start
in my hometown in 1988.

00:03:02.050 --> 00:03:03.084 position:35% line:89% align:start
Say what?

00:03:03.117 --> 00:03:05.053 position:7% line:89% align:start
It would seem, this freak show

00:03:05.086 --> 00:03:07.454 position:16% line:83% align:start
represents the dark side
of my heart.

00:03:07.487 --> 00:03:09.991 position:27% line:83% align:start
Your memories...
They really are back.

00:03:10.024 --> 00:03:11.793 position:5% line:89% align:start
So you remember everything now?

00:03:13.027 --> 00:03:16.263 position:13% line:83% align:start
Then get your act together
and do something about this!

00:03:16.296 --> 00:03:18.498 position:10% line:83% align:start
[Weather] I have no control
over this ability.

00:03:18.533 --> 00:03:20.835 position:19% line:83% align:start
Though if you kill me,
the Stand's power should stop.

00:03:20.868 --> 00:03:21.769 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:03:21.803 --> 00:03:24.237 position:16% line:83% align:start
I do kinda feel bad for
the snail people,

00:03:24.271 --> 00:03:26.708 position:27% line:83% align:start
but a part of me
hates living even more,

00:03:26.741 --> 00:03:29.677 position:13% line:83% align:start
and that part is enjoying
the hell out of this.

00:03:29.711 --> 00:03:32.212 position:24% line:83% align:start
Somewhere down in
the deepest recesses

00:03:32.245 --> 00:03:33.781 position:33% line:83% align:start
of my heart,
I feel some relief.

00:03:33.815 --> 00:03:36.017 position:30% line:83% align:start
To be honest,
I'm sort of glad this happened.

00:03:36.050 --> 00:03:36.951 position:27% line:89% align:start
What are you...?

00:03:36.984 --> 00:03:38.318 position:27% line:83% align:start
-[snails splurt]
-Huh.

00:03:40.521 --> 00:03:43.124 position:7% line:89% align:start
But Jolyne... If she's nearby,

00:03:43.157 --> 00:03:45.126 position:21% line:83% align:start
could she be turning
into a snail too?

00:03:45.159 --> 00:03:46.828 position:27% line:83% align:start
You'd better not
move carelessly.

00:03:47.695 --> 00:03:49.964 position:30% line:83% align:start
I have no idea
how all this works,

00:03:49.997 --> 00:03:51.699 position:33% line:83% align:start
but judging
by what I can see,

00:03:51.733 --> 00:03:53.433 position:13% line:83% align:start
it's likely that touching
these snails

00:03:53.467 --> 00:03:55.103 position:24% line:83% align:start
is the trigger to
this phenomenon.

00:03:55.136 --> 00:03:55.970 position:24% line:89% align:start
[Anastasia gasps]

00:03:56.003 --> 00:03:58.172 position:10% line:89% align:start
Moreover, if you turn snail,

00:03:58.206 --> 00:03:59.607 position:16% line:83% align:start
there'll be no one left
to kill me.

00:03:59.640 --> 00:04:00.307 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:04:00.340 --> 00:04:01.642 position:7% line:89% align:start
What kind of fucking nonsense

00:04:01.676 --> 00:04:03.343 position:10% line:83% align:start
is coming out of your mouth,
you bastard?

00:04:03.376 --> 00:04:06.681 position:7% line:83% align:start
I don't wanna hear it. Tell me
where Jolyne is right now!

00:04:06.714 --> 00:04:09.817 position:13% line:83% align:start
Yeah, fine, but only after
we settle things with Pucchi.

00:04:09.851 --> 00:04:11.451 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Uh.
-I told you,

00:04:11.485 --> 00:04:13.821 position:19% line:83% align:start
that so-called priest
is somewhere nearby.

00:04:13.855 --> 00:04:14.387 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:04:15.089 --> 00:04:16.824 position:21% line:89% align:start
What? Really, where?

00:04:17.625 --> 00:04:18.693 position:35% line:89% align:start
He's here.

00:04:18.726 --> 00:04:21.495 position:30% line:83% align:start
At this point,
my only hope for staying alive

00:04:21.529 --> 00:04:23.998 position:7% line:83% align:start
is to settle things between us
once and for all.

00:04:24.565 --> 00:04:25.332 position:38% line:89% align:start
[scoffs]

00:04:25.365 --> 00:04:27.201 position:13% line:89% align:start
From what happened to FF,

00:04:27.235 --> 00:04:29.537 position:27% line:83% align:start
to sealing away
Jolyne's father's memories

00:04:29.570 --> 00:04:32.206 position:10% line:83% align:start
for his own selfish desires
to come to fruition,

00:04:32.240 --> 00:04:34.041 position:21% line:89% align:start
I'll settle it all.

00:04:34.075 --> 00:04:35.810 position:5% line:89% align:start
I'll be the one to kill Pucchi.

00:04:35.843 --> 00:04:37.545 position:24% line:89% align:start
[Anastasia gasps]

00:04:37.578 --> 00:04:39.647 position:10% line:83% align:start
And once he's taken care of,
you'll kill me.

00:04:39.981 --> 00:04:40.882 position:38% line:89% align:start
Got it?

00:04:40.915 --> 00:04:42.917 position:38% line:83% align:start
[scoffs]
Fine, whatever.

00:04:42.950 --> 00:04:46.721 position:13% line:83% align:start
I still owe FF a big one,
anyways. I'm with you.

00:04:46.754 --> 00:04:48.923 position:24% line:83% align:start
Speaking of which,
where is the priest?

00:04:48.956 --> 00:04:50.057 position:19% line:89% align:start
Is he north or south?

00:04:50.091 --> 00:04:52.527 position:30% line:83% align:start
It isn't about
where he's coming from.

00:04:52.560 --> 00:04:54.662 position:16% line:89% align:start
The man's already here.

00:04:54.695 --> 00:04:56.931 position:24% line:83% align:start
And he's somewhere
within 20 meters of us.

00:04:58.465 --> 00:05:00.835 position:5% line:83% align:start
I've already done a quick sweep
for him underground

00:05:00.868 --> 00:05:01.969 position:19% line:89% align:start
using my Diver Drive.

00:05:03.037 --> 00:05:05.405 position:5% line:89% align:start
All I can see are these snails.

00:05:05.438 --> 00:05:07.942 position:7% line:83% align:start
Are you positive he's closing
in on us through all this?

00:05:10.111 --> 00:05:12.046 position:38% line:83% align:start
[gasps]
Weather Forecast!

00:05:15.750 --> 00:05:17.417 position:27% line:89% align:start
[dramatic music]

00:05:19.620 --> 00:05:22.422 position:19% line:83% align:start
There's no disturbance
in the air currents.

00:05:22.455 --> 00:05:24.424 position:13% line:83% align:start
And I don't sense anything
in the area

00:05:24.457 --> 00:05:25.827 position:10% line:89% align:start
breathing or moving around.

00:05:26.260 --> 00:05:27.061 position:33% line:89% align:start
[both gasp]

00:05:28.729 --> 00:05:31.065 position:5% line:83% align:start
[Anastasia] What if he's hiding
inside that car, Weather?

00:05:31.666 --> 00:05:32.332 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hm.

00:05:33.968 --> 00:05:35.136 position:41% line:89% align:start
Mm-hm.

00:05:35.169 --> 00:05:37.071 position:30% line:89% align:start
[eerie music]

00:05:56.157 --> 00:05:57.357 position:27% line:89% align:start
[grunts in pain]

00:05:58.926 --> 00:05:59.927 position:35% line:89% align:start
[exclaims]

00:06:03.297 --> 00:06:04.464 position:21% line:89% align:start
[Anastasia] Weather!

00:06:04.866 --> 00:06:05.867 position:35% line:89% align:start
[shudders]

00:06:05.900 --> 00:06:07.902 position:27% line:89% align:start
[grunts in pain]

00:06:07.935 --> 00:06:09.537 position:27% line:83% align:start
[Father Pucchi]
I am already well aware

00:06:09.570 --> 00:06:12.506 position:5% line:83% align:start
of how that weather-controlling
ability of yours functions.

00:06:13.708 --> 00:06:15.977 position:21% line:83% align:start
This phenomenon that
turns anything,

00:06:16.010 --> 00:06:18.546 position:13% line:89% align:start
man or beast, into snails,

00:06:18.579 --> 00:06:21.582 position:10% line:83% align:start
as long as I understand the
secret behind why it happens...

00:06:21.616 --> 00:06:23.217 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[gasps]
-[snails clatter]

00:06:23.251 --> 00:06:24.585 position:10% line:89% align:start
I have absolutely no reason

00:06:24.619 --> 00:06:27.121 position:13% line:83% align:start
to be afraid of the snails
touching my body!

00:06:27.154 --> 00:06:28.956 position:7% line:89% align:start
I've uncovered how this works.

00:06:28.990 --> 00:06:31.158 position:21% line:83% align:start
Although it took me
a while to figure out

00:06:31.192 --> 00:06:33.060 position:16% line:83% align:start
the specific intricacies
of your ability,

00:06:33.094 --> 00:06:35.329 position:7% line:89% align:start
I have overcome it once before

00:06:35.363 --> 00:06:37.865 position:30% line:83% align:start
when I removed
your memories in 1988!

00:06:37.899 --> 00:06:39.000 position:27% line:89% align:start
You son of a...

00:06:39.033 --> 00:06:41.535 position:24% line:89% align:start
Damn you, Pucchi!

00:06:42.036 --> 00:06:42.937 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:06:42.970 --> 00:06:44.404 position:19% line:89% align:start
[snail slime gurgles]

00:06:46.007 --> 00:06:47.008 position:38% line:89% align:start
[groans]

00:06:48.242 --> 00:06:49.476 position:27% line:89% align:start
[Narciso gasps]

00:06:49.510 --> 00:06:51.913 position:27% line:83% align:start
[Father Pucchi]
It's all over for you now, too.

00:06:51.946 --> 00:06:53.281 position:21% line:83% align:start
You should've stayed
out of my business

00:06:53.314 --> 00:06:55.149 position:19% line:89% align:start
and away from Jolyne.

00:06:55.182 --> 00:06:56.250 position:30% line:83% align:start
but instead of
patiently waiting

00:06:56.284 --> 00:06:58.019 position:16% line:83% align:start
for your prison sentence
to end,

00:06:58.052 --> 00:06:59.053 position:5% line:89% align:start
you chose to end your own life.

00:06:59.820 --> 00:07:00.655 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:07:00.688 --> 00:07:01.789 position:10% line:89% align:start
[Anastasia] I don't get it.

00:07:01.822 --> 00:07:04.592 position:30% line:83% align:start
How is Pucchi
standing there unscathed?

00:07:04.625 --> 00:07:06.794 position:16% line:83% align:start
These snails don't make
any sense.

00:07:06.827 --> 00:07:08.461 position:7% line:89% align:start
What's going on here, Weather?

00:07:08.963 --> 00:07:10.932 position:21% line:89% align:start
[gasping continues]

00:07:10.965 --> 00:07:12.867 position:27% line:83% align:start
[Father Pucchi]
With this, let's call it good.

00:07:12.900 --> 00:07:13.935 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:07:13.968 --> 00:07:17.038 position:13% line:83% align:start
If you're planning to die
sometime soon, Weather,

00:07:17.071 --> 00:07:18.639 position:19% line:89% align:start
hold off for a while.

00:07:18.673 --> 00:07:19.840 position:21% line:89% align:start
I cut your leg off,

00:07:19.874 --> 00:07:22.877 position:16% line:83% align:start
so it'd take a few hours
for you to bleed out.

00:07:22.910 --> 00:07:25.546 position:10% line:83% align:start
With this deadly phenomenon
you caused still in play,

00:07:25.579 --> 00:07:26.847 position:7% line:89% align:start
it will be the perfect weapon

00:07:26.881 --> 00:07:28.349 position:33% line:83% align:start
for putting
an end to all nuisances

00:07:28.382 --> 00:07:30.384 position:13% line:89% align:start
who attempt to oppose me.

00:07:30.418 --> 00:07:31.786 position:27% line:89% align:start
[Weather groans]

00:07:31.819 --> 00:07:35.089 position:19% line:83% align:start
I now know who will be
raising me up to attain heaven.

00:07:35.122 --> 00:07:38.025 position:38% line:83% align:start
Weather,
it turns out to be you,

00:07:38.059 --> 00:07:39.694 position:27% line:89% align:start
not anyone else.

00:07:39.727 --> 00:07:40.094 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:07:41.562 --> 00:07:43.197 position:21% line:89% align:start
[breathing shakily]

00:07:44.198 --> 00:07:46.499 position:35% line:89% align:start
[screams]

00:07:46.534 --> 00:07:49.337 position:16% line:83% align:start
We still have three days
until the new moon arrives,

00:07:49.370 --> 00:07:51.706 position:5% line:89% align:start
and then it will finally begin.

00:07:51.739 --> 00:07:55.009 position:7% line:83% align:start
The moment that the Green Baby
desired will come to pass,

00:07:55.042 --> 00:07:57.812 position:5% line:83% align:start
and the manifestation of heaven
that Dio strived for

00:07:57.845 --> 00:07:59.814 position:30% line:83% align:start
will take root
inside of my body.

00:08:00.514 --> 00:08:01.649 position:21% line:83% align:start
-[thuds in distance]
-Hm?

00:08:02.216 --> 00:08:02.783 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:08:04.752 --> 00:08:05.485 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:08:07.521 --> 00:08:10.091 position:24% line:83% align:start
With Diver Drive,
I gave Weather a leg...

00:08:10.124 --> 00:08:11.025 position:19% line:89% align:start
[Diver Drive chitters]

00:08:11.058 --> 00:08:12.893 position:33% line:83% align:start
[Anastasia]
...by phasing into his body!

00:08:12.927 --> 00:08:15.196 position:24% line:89% align:start
Weather Forecast!

00:08:15.229 --> 00:08:16.364 position:35% line:83% align:start
-[grunts]
-[crashes]

00:08:16.397 --> 00:08:17.765 position:33% line:83% align:start
-[squelches]
-[yelps]

00:08:18.399 --> 00:08:19.233 position:35% line:83% align:start
-[grunts]
-[smashes]

00:08:19.266 --> 00:08:21.335 position:35% line:89% align:start
[retches]

00:08:21.369 --> 00:08:24.238 position:10% line:83% align:start
[Anastasia] Wrap the priest
and bring him closer, Weather!

00:08:24.271 --> 00:08:27.108 position:16% line:83% align:start
Your big brother's Stand
isn't a power type like yours.

00:08:27.141 --> 00:08:28.909 position:7% line:89% align:start
If you can keep ahold of him,

00:08:28.943 --> 00:08:30.845 position:21% line:83% align:start
you can outmatch him
at point-blank range!

00:08:31.245 --> 00:08:32.546 position:35% line:89% align:start
Grab him,

00:08:32.580 --> 00:08:34.548 position:24% line:83% align:start
and don't you dare
let him get away!

00:08:34.582 --> 00:08:35.583 position:35% line:89% align:start
[whooshes]

00:08:36.617 --> 00:08:39.253 position:24% line:89% align:start
[grandiose music]

00:08:39.987 --> 00:08:40.855 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:08:41.822 --> 00:08:42.790 position:41% line:89% align:start
What?

00:08:44.191 --> 00:08:44.959 position:27% line:89% align:start
[Weather groans]

00:08:44.992 --> 00:08:46.093 position:38% line:89% align:start
Weather!

00:08:46.127 --> 00:08:47.094 position:27% line:89% align:start
[Weather groans]

00:08:47.128 --> 00:08:48.996 position:10% line:89% align:start
Damn it, what just happened?

00:08:49.030 --> 00:08:51.465 position:10% line:83% align:start
I wasn't even anywhere near
touching the snails!

00:08:51.499 --> 00:08:52.466 position:38% line:89% align:start
Pucchi!

00:08:52.500 --> 00:08:54.568 position:24% line:83% align:start
What sort of game
are you playing?

00:08:54.602 --> 00:08:55.936 position:13% line:89% align:start
What the hell did you do?

00:08:56.537 --> 00:08:57.938 position:19% line:89% align:start
Subliminal messaging.

00:08:57.972 --> 00:08:59.508 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:08:59.540 --> 00:09:01.142 position:13% line:83% align:start
[Father Pucchi] The method
of cleverly arranging

00:09:01.175 --> 00:09:02.309 position:16% line:89% align:start
hidden words on a poster

00:09:02.343 --> 00:09:04.745 position:19% line:83% align:start
that cannot be noticed
at first glance,

00:09:04.779 --> 00:09:06.847 position:10% line:83% align:start
or a single frame containing
an image that has been clipped

00:09:06.881 --> 00:09:08.783 position:13% line:89% align:start
into the film of a movie,

00:09:08.816 --> 00:09:12.053 position:7% line:83% align:start
the average person is unaware
of ever having seen the image,

00:09:12.086 --> 00:09:13.721 position:21% line:83% align:start
but without a doubt,
it becomes carved

00:09:13.754 --> 00:09:16.257 position:7% line:83% align:start
into their deep consciousness
and lingers there.

00:09:16.290 --> 00:09:19.528 position:5% line:83% align:start
That's what psychologists refer
to as subliminal messaging

00:09:19.560 --> 00:09:22.363 position:19% line:83% align:start
and the effect it has
on the subconscious.

00:09:22.396 --> 00:09:24.198 position:27% line:83% align:start
Things or images
that are instinctive

00:09:24.231 --> 00:09:26.400 position:19% line:83% align:start
penetrate much further
into one's consciousness

00:09:26.434 --> 00:09:28.302 position:24% line:83% align:start
more than if they
are witnessed directly.

00:09:28.335 --> 00:09:29.670 position:16% line:89% align:start
And as a result of this,

00:09:29.703 --> 00:09:32.541 position:5% line:83% align:start
they control what an individual
may decide to do.

00:09:32.573 --> 00:09:34.308 position:19% line:83% align:start
And now, the rainbows
Weather Forecast conjured

00:09:34.341 --> 00:09:35.876 position:10% line:89% align:start
are having that same effect,

00:09:35.910 --> 00:09:37.278 position:30% line:83% align:start
it's becoming
a subliminal message

00:09:37.311 --> 00:09:38.979 position:16% line:89% align:start
at an atmospheric level.

00:09:39.013 --> 00:09:40.681 position:19% line:83% align:start
And whenever they lay
their eyes on them,

00:09:40.714 --> 00:09:43.384 position:16% line:83% align:start
it's entering the souls
of the townspeople!

00:09:43.417 --> 00:09:46.787 position:7% line:83% align:start
Is it because images of snails
are being projected onto them?

00:09:46.821 --> 00:09:50.291 position:13% line:83% align:start
Or could it be because it
stimulates primitive instincts?

00:09:50.324 --> 00:09:52.527 position:24% line:83% align:start
Everyone who looks
at the rainbow starts to think

00:09:52.561 --> 00:09:55.129 position:30% line:83% align:start
that they too
will become snails.

00:09:55.162 --> 00:09:56.597 position:13% line:89% align:start
And these intense thoughts

00:09:56.630 --> 00:09:59.033 position:21% line:83% align:start
affect the subjects
physically as well.

00:09:59.066 --> 00:09:59.867 position:24% line:89% align:start
What the hell...?

00:09:59.900 --> 00:10:01.669 position:21% line:83% align:start
What are you trying
to explain here?

00:10:01.702 --> 00:10:03.637 position:16% line:89% align:start
This is the true answer.

00:10:03.671 --> 00:10:04.905 position:10% line:89% align:start
The truth behind the ability

00:10:04.939 --> 00:10:07.374 position:27% line:83% align:start
Weather Forecast
had sealed away.

00:10:07.408 --> 00:10:09.009 position:33% line:83% align:start
In the past,
when the same phenomenon

00:10:09.043 --> 00:10:11.812 position:5% line:83% align:start
occurred to the innocent people
in my hometown,

00:10:11.846 --> 00:10:14.882 position:10% line:83% align:start
I saw that a blind old woman
was completely unaffected,

00:10:14.915 --> 00:10:16.717 position:27% line:83% align:start
and that's when
I understood the solution

00:10:16.750 --> 00:10:18.352 position:24% line:83% align:start
to getting rid of
the strange occurrence.

00:10:19.153 --> 00:10:21.222 position:16% line:89% align:start
Being blind, you get...

00:10:21.255 --> 00:10:22.123 position:16% line:89% align:start
[Father Pucchi] Weather,

00:10:22.156 --> 00:10:24.425 position:21% line:83% align:start
even if I can't see,
I can still sense

00:10:24.458 --> 00:10:25.960 position:30% line:83% align:start
where you are
with my intuition.

00:10:25.993 --> 00:10:26.827 position:33% line:89% align:start
[both gasp]

00:10:26.861 --> 00:10:28.429 position:7% line:89% align:start
And this will work long after

00:10:28.462 --> 00:10:30.664 position:16% line:83% align:start
I've removed my ability
to use my eyes.

00:10:30.698 --> 00:10:31.999 position:21% line:89% align:start
But let me tell you.

00:10:32.032 --> 00:10:35.169 position:19% line:83% align:start
Closing your eyes now
will not save you, Anastasia.

00:10:35.202 --> 00:10:37.572 position:13% line:83% align:start
There is no way to escape
from the subliminal messaging

00:10:37.606 --> 00:10:40.207 position:13% line:83% align:start
once it has dug its roots
into your soul.

00:10:40.241 --> 00:10:42.511 position:10% line:83% align:start
As long as Weather continues
to draw breath,

00:10:42.544 --> 00:10:45.112 position:10% line:83% align:start
this destructive phenomenon
will never end!

00:10:45.146 --> 00:10:47.148 position:24% line:89% align:start
[Weather strains]

00:10:47.181 --> 00:10:49.450 position:24% line:83% align:start
I think I'll take
your other leg as well.

00:10:49.483 --> 00:10:50.451 position:33% line:89% align:start
[squelches]

00:10:50.484 --> 00:10:51.452 position:30% line:89% align:start
[choked gasp]

00:10:51.485 --> 00:10:53.654 position:24% line:89% align:start
[grumbles in pain]

00:10:53.687 --> 00:10:55.524 position:27% line:83% align:start
[Father Pucchi]
You will not stand ever again!

00:10:55.557 --> 00:10:56.924 position:33% line:89% align:start
Diver Drive!

00:10:56.957 --> 00:10:58.392 position:7% line:89% align:start
Don't you dare lash out at me

00:10:58.425 --> 00:11:00.261 position:16% line:83% align:start
with your insignificant
feelings!

00:11:00.294 --> 00:11:01.061 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:11:02.730 --> 00:11:03.697 position:27% line:83% align:start
[Father Pucchi]
Humans must strive

00:11:03.731 --> 00:11:05.432 position:7% line:89% align:start
to reach the gates of heaven.

00:11:05.466 --> 00:11:07.636 position:10% line:83% align:start
And the one who is the first
to find and attain it

00:11:07.668 --> 00:11:09.770 position:21% line:83% align:start
will be able to lead
all of mankind to it!

00:11:09.803 --> 00:11:12.706 position:7% line:83% align:start
You two are merely interfering
with my progress,

00:11:12.740 --> 00:11:14.008 position:5% line:89% align:start
all because I have to sacrifice

00:11:14.041 --> 00:11:16.545 position:13% line:83% align:start
the lives of a few people
to do so!

00:11:16.578 --> 00:11:18.746 position:24% line:89% align:start
Domine quo vadis?

00:11:18.779 --> 00:11:20.381 position:27% line:89% align:start
To be crucified,

00:11:20.414 --> 00:11:22.416 position:19% line:89% align:start
now die for your sins!

00:11:22.449 --> 00:11:23.751 position:33% line:83% align:start
-[squelches]
-[Father Pucchi grunts]

00:11:23.784 --> 00:11:25.587 position:27% line:83% align:start
-[Narciso gasps]
-W-What the...?

00:11:25.620 --> 00:11:27.221 position:35% line:89% align:start
[strains]

00:11:27.254 --> 00:11:29.524 position:24% line:83% align:start
-[blood spatters]
-[Father Pucchi groans]

00:11:29.558 --> 00:11:31.725 position:5% line:89% align:start
What is this? What's happening?

00:11:31.759 --> 00:11:34.128 position:35% line:89% align:start
[scraping]

00:11:34.161 --> 00:11:36.397 position:21% line:83% align:start
This is your doing,
isn't it, Weather?

00:11:36.430 --> 00:11:37.965 position:16% line:89% align:start
What are you up to now?

00:11:37.998 --> 00:11:40.267 position:19% line:83% align:start
What is this atrocious
scraping sound?

00:11:40.301 --> 00:11:42.504 position:30% line:83% align:start
What on earth
do you think you're doing?

00:11:42.537 --> 00:11:44.639 position:7% line:89% align:start
Something that I can control.

00:11:44.673 --> 00:11:47.775 position:13% line:83% align:start
One of Weather Forecast's
abilities.

00:11:48.442 --> 00:11:50.244 position:10% line:89% align:start
It doesn't have to be fast,

00:11:50.277 --> 00:11:51.946 position:10% line:83% align:start
-but if I make it precise...
-[scraping]

00:11:51.979 --> 00:11:53.714 position:7% line:89% align:start
...and if I keep it simple...

00:11:54.715 --> 00:11:56.183 position:33% line:83% align:start
[Anastasia]
He's evaporating his blood,

00:11:56.217 --> 00:11:58.285 position:19% line:83% align:start
freezing it in the air
and hardening it.

00:11:58.319 --> 00:12:00.321 position:7% line:83% align:start
Weather's using all the blood
on the ground

00:12:00.354 --> 00:12:01.623 position:10% line:89% align:start
to surround him with spears,

00:12:01.656 --> 00:12:03.457 position:30% line:83% align:start
and the priest
can't even see it!

00:12:03.490 --> 00:12:05.459 position:7% line:89% align:start
So what are you gonna choose?

00:12:05.492 --> 00:12:06.860 position:21% line:83% align:start
You have the option
to continue this

00:12:06.894 --> 00:12:08.429 position:5% line:89% align:start
without the use of your vision.

00:12:08.462 --> 00:12:10.931 position:21% line:83% align:start
And the other option
that you have to choose from

00:12:10.965 --> 00:12:13.300 position:13% line:83% align:start
is seeing what's going on
with your own eyes.

00:12:13.334 --> 00:12:16.036 position:13% line:83% align:start
But if you trip and fall,
it's over for you.

00:12:16.070 --> 00:12:16.203 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:12:17.572 --> 00:12:18.138 position:35% line:89% align:start
[grumbles]

00:12:20.341 --> 00:12:21.809 position:21% line:89% align:start
Here I come, Pucchi.

00:12:22.743 --> 00:12:23.911 position:35% line:89% align:start
Get ready.

00:12:26.548 --> 00:12:28.382 position:27% line:89% align:start
[dramatic music]

00:12:30.518 --> 00:12:32.286 position:35% line:89% align:start
[strains]

00:12:32.319 --> 00:12:33.821 position:21% line:89% align:start
You're done, Pucchi.

00:12:33.854 --> 00:12:35.956 position:10% line:83% align:start
There's no way you're gonna
escape from this.

00:12:35.990 --> 00:12:37.692 position:21% line:83% align:start
Are you gonna bring
your eyesight back?

00:12:37.726 --> 00:12:39.026 position:24% line:89% align:start
Go ahead and try!

00:12:39.059 --> 00:12:41.762 position:7% line:83% align:start
I'll just reflect the rainbows
straight into your face!

00:12:41.795 --> 00:12:42.896 position:16% line:89% align:start
If Weather can grab you,

00:12:42.930 --> 00:12:45.332 position:16% line:83% align:start
your chances of survival
are slim to none!

00:12:45.366 --> 00:12:47.901 position:7% line:83% align:start
In terms of power, Pale Snake
is simply outclassed!

00:12:48.769 --> 00:12:50.538 position:7% line:89% align:start
Weather's got this in the bag!

00:12:50.572 --> 00:12:51.939 position:38% line:89% align:start
[scoffs]

00:12:51.972 --> 00:12:54.709 position:19% line:83% align:start
I anticipated that you
would try to do something.

00:12:54.743 --> 00:12:56.143 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:12:56.176 --> 00:12:57.311 position:27% line:83% align:start
[Father Pucchi]
There is not a reality

00:12:57.344 --> 00:12:59.547 position:21% line:83% align:start
where you would ever
let me go peacefully.

00:12:59.581 --> 00:13:02.550 position:7% line:83% align:start
You, who has finally regained
his lost memories...

00:13:02.584 --> 00:13:03.384 position:27% line:89% align:start
[Weather grunts]

00:13:03.417 --> 00:13:04.418 position:16% line:89% align:start
[Father Pucchi] However!

00:13:04.451 --> 00:13:06.220 position:24% line:83% align:start
-[blood sputters]
-[chokes]

00:13:06.621 --> 00:13:07.888 position:35% line:89% align:start
Anastasia!

00:13:07.921 --> 00:13:10.659 position:19% line:83% align:start
There are eyes for me
to see out of from all over.

00:13:10.692 --> 00:13:12.226 position:19% line:83% align:start
That's how I was able
to come here.

00:13:12.259 --> 00:13:15.296 position:16% line:83% align:start
Anastasia, may I use you
for a moment?

00:13:15.329 --> 00:13:18.432 position:7% line:83% align:start
You shall act as a substitute
for my eyes.

00:13:18.465 --> 00:13:21.468 position:7% line:83% align:start
Would you kindly relate to me
what you see in front of you?

00:13:21.503 --> 00:13:24.539 position:16% line:83% align:start
Specifically, the things
that are dangerous to me.

00:13:24.572 --> 00:13:26.373 position:19% line:83% align:start
What is Weather doing
currently?

00:13:28.743 --> 00:13:30.144 position:30% line:83% align:start
He's hardening
his own blood to create

00:13:30.177 --> 00:13:33.213 position:10% line:83% align:start
a few dozen spears all over
the ground around you.

00:13:33.247 --> 00:13:35.949 position:16% line:83% align:start
There are three of them
placed directly behind you.

00:13:35.983 --> 00:13:38.419 position:7% line:83% align:start
Then to your right, there are
four more lying in wait.

00:13:38.452 --> 00:13:38.852 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:13:39.521 --> 00:13:40.588 position:41% line:89% align:start
I see.

00:13:40.622 --> 00:13:42.557 position:24% line:83% align:start
Now, be a good boy
and guide me out

00:13:42.590 --> 00:13:43.991 position:33% line:83% align:start
of this maze
of blood spears, okay?

00:13:44.726 --> 00:13:46.360 position:27% line:89% align:start
Please continue.

00:13:46.393 --> 00:13:48.962 position:16% line:83% align:start
If you take three steps,
you will meet six spears.

00:13:48.996 --> 00:13:51.098 position:7% line:83% align:start
From there, you're gonna want
to take a hard left.

00:13:54.201 --> 00:13:55.302 position:38% line:89% align:start
Weather.

00:13:55.336 --> 00:13:57.104 position:21% line:83% align:start
From the very moment
you were born,

00:13:57.137 --> 00:13:58.405 position:13% line:89% align:start
a curse has afflicted you.

00:13:58.439 --> 00:14:00.007 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:14:00.040 --> 00:14:02.644 position:13% line:83% align:start
[Father Pucchi] Stay there
silently, just as you are.

00:14:02.677 --> 00:14:04.144 position:30% line:83% align:start
No matter what
you attempt to do,

00:14:04.178 --> 00:14:06.013 position:19% line:83% align:start
there is no salvation
for your life.

00:14:06.914 --> 00:14:08.282 position:13% line:89% align:start
The memories I sealed away

00:14:08.315 --> 00:14:10.685 position:5% line:83% align:start
should never have been returned
to you in the first place.

00:14:10.719 --> 00:14:12.019 position:38% line:89% align:start
[snarls]

00:14:12.052 --> 00:14:14.922 position:16% line:83% align:start
Continue going left for
five steps, then face right.

00:14:14.955 --> 00:14:17.124 position:16% line:83% align:start
After that, you're free
from any danger.

00:14:17.157 --> 00:14:19.426 position:13% line:89% align:start
Splendid. Five more steps.

00:14:19.460 --> 00:14:21.596 position:21% line:89% align:start
Correct. Just five.

00:14:21.629 --> 00:14:23.598 position:24% line:83% align:start
This is something
I just realized.

00:14:23.631 --> 00:14:25.432 position:5% line:89% align:start
But I saw it, so I'll tell you.

00:14:26.166 --> 00:14:28.068 position:7% line:89% align:start
One more spear still remains.

00:14:28.102 --> 00:14:29.269 position:21% line:89% align:start
[Father Pucchi] Hmm?

00:14:29.303 --> 00:14:30.739 position:24% line:83% align:start
I was only looking
at the ground,

00:14:30.772 --> 00:14:31.939 position:13% line:89% align:start
