00:14:32.841 --> 00:14:34.441 position:24% line:83% align:start
There's some blood
on your shoulder.

00:14:35.109 --> 00:14:36.243 position:21% line:89% align:start
And right about now,

00:14:36.276 --> 00:14:38.045 position:19% line:83% align:start
Weather's hardening it
into another spear.

00:14:38.813 --> 00:14:40.582 position:21% line:89% align:start
Oops, it's too late.

00:14:41.783 --> 00:14:43.150 position:24% line:89% align:start
[screams in agony]

00:14:43.183 --> 00:14:45.085 position:5% line:89% align:start
You planned these dirty tricks!

00:14:45.119 --> 00:14:45.787 position:38% line:89% align:start
[thuds]

00:14:45.820 --> 00:14:47.822 position:5% line:89% align:start
Like hell any of this is dirty!

00:14:47.856 --> 00:14:49.591 position:16% line:83% align:start
Weather is just stronger
than you,

00:14:49.624 --> 00:14:51.793 position:7% line:89% align:start
and that's why he's gonna win!

00:14:51.826 --> 00:14:53.661 position:16% line:89% align:start
[Father Pucchi grumbles]

00:14:53.695 --> 00:14:56.731 position:38% line:83% align:start
[grunts]
This wind pressure's so...

00:14:56.765 --> 00:14:58.733 position:33% line:83% align:start
I-I must get
as far away as I can

00:14:58.767 --> 00:15:00.568 position:24% line:83% align:start
from the range of
his Stand immediately!

00:15:00.602 --> 00:15:01.803 position:19% line:89% align:start
[Father Pucchi grunts]

00:15:01.836 --> 00:15:03.638 position:7% line:89% align:start
I have to dodge just one blow.

00:15:03.671 --> 00:15:04.839 position:24% line:89% align:start
If I can dodge it,

00:15:04.873 --> 00:15:06.808 position:19% line:83% align:start
then Weather's stamina
should reach his limits!

00:15:06.841 --> 00:15:09.443 position:35% line:89% align:start
[burbles]

00:15:09.476 --> 00:15:12.012 position:33% line:83% align:start
Get impaled
by your own blood spears!

00:15:12.045 --> 00:15:13.648 position:16% line:89% align:start
It's useless to resist!

00:15:13.681 --> 00:15:15.149 position:19% line:83% align:start
That attack's nothing
to Weather.

00:15:15.182 --> 00:15:17.084 position:16% line:89% align:start
He can dodge it easily!

00:15:17.117 --> 00:15:19.286 position:21% line:83% align:start
[Father Pucchi] Yes,
I have no doubt that he will.

00:15:19.319 --> 00:15:21.823 position:13% line:83% align:start
But then, the direction of
his wind pressure will change.

00:15:21.856 --> 00:15:23.123 position:13% line:89% align:start
That's my chance to flee!

00:15:23.858 --> 00:15:25.192 position:33% line:89% align:start
[whooshing]

00:15:25.225 --> 00:15:26.393 position:35% line:89% align:start
[gasping]

00:15:26.427 --> 00:15:27.327 position:16% line:89% align:start
[Weather] I've got you.

00:15:29.664 --> 00:15:31.533 position:13% line:89% align:start
I've finally got you now.

00:15:31.566 --> 00:15:33.066 position:35% line:89% align:start
[strains]

00:15:33.100 --> 00:15:34.301 position:33% line:83% align:start
[Anastasia]
He didn't dodge them.

00:15:34.334 --> 00:15:35.837 position:19% line:83% align:start
Weather actually took
the spears

00:15:35.870 --> 00:15:37.471 position:30% line:83% align:start
and used them
to capture the priest!

00:15:37.505 --> 00:15:38.873 position:35% line:89% align:start
[strains]

00:15:38.907 --> 00:15:40.207 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:15:40.240 --> 00:15:42.109 position:33% line:83% align:start
[Anastasia]
He's within Weather's range!

00:15:43.210 --> 00:15:44.978 position:38% line:89% align:start
[snarls]

00:15:45.012 --> 00:15:46.614 position:33% line:89% align:start
[inaudible]

00:15:48.382 --> 00:15:51.018 position:30% line:89% align:start
[both scream]

00:15:52.219 --> 00:15:52.986 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gags]

00:15:54.354 --> 00:15:55.289 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:15:55.322 --> 00:15:56.156 position:27% line:89% align:start
Did he get him?

00:15:57.592 --> 00:15:58.593 position:19% line:89% align:start
[Father Pucchi grunts]

00:15:58.626 --> 00:16:01.462 position:16% line:89% align:start
Don't do it, W-Weather.

00:16:01.495 --> 00:16:04.097 position:30% line:83% align:start
While you were
in Green Dolphin Street Prison,

00:16:04.131 --> 00:16:05.966 position:10% line:83% align:start
I could've finished you off
at any given moment

00:16:05.999 --> 00:16:07.669 position:19% line:89% align:start
if I truly wanted to.

00:16:07.702 --> 00:16:11.305 position:7% line:83% align:start
Except... I had it in my head
that one day I could save you,

00:16:11.338 --> 00:16:13.708 position:33% line:83% align:start
which is why
I stole your memories!

00:16:13.741 --> 00:16:15.643 position:27% line:83% align:start
This isn't some
convenient excuse

00:16:15.677 --> 00:16:17.211 position:10% line:89% align:start
if I'm begging for my life!

00:16:17.244 --> 00:16:19.514 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:16:19.547 --> 00:16:21.516 position:5% line:83% align:start
-[Father Pucchi] Prime numbers.
-Listen to me, brother.

00:16:21.549 --> 00:16:23.217 position:10% line:83% align:start
-I did all of this for you.
-[Father Pucchi] One.

00:16:23.250 --> 00:16:24.318 position:41% line:89% align:start
Three.

00:16:24.351 --> 00:16:26.119 position:10% line:83% align:start
I worked tirelessly towards
my goal of attaining...

00:16:26.153 --> 00:16:26.987 position:19% line:83% align:start
-[Father Pucchi] Five.
-...immense power

00:16:27.020 --> 00:16:28.623 position:5% line:89% align:start
so that both of us can prosper.

00:16:28.656 --> 00:16:29.557 position:19% line:89% align:start
There must be someone

00:16:29.591 --> 00:16:31.058 position:33% line:83% align:start
who obtains
the power to reach heaven.

00:16:31.091 --> 00:16:32.993 position:33% line:83% align:start
It was fated
to happen eventually!

00:16:33.026 --> 00:16:33.628 position:19% line:89% align:start
[Father Pucchi] Seven.

00:16:34.995 --> 00:16:36.196 position:24% line:89% align:start
-Stop it, Weather.

00:16:36.230 --> 00:16:37.565 position:16% line:89% align:start
[Father Pucchi] Eleven.

00:16:37.599 --> 00:16:38.833 position:13% line:83% align:start
-This is certain to put...
-[Father Pucchi] Thirteen.

00:16:38.867 --> 00:16:40.133 position:33% line:83% align:start
...an end to
both of our lives!

00:16:41.669 --> 00:16:42.637 position:13% line:89% align:start
[Father Pucchi] Seventeen.

00:16:42.670 --> 00:16:44.338 position:10% line:89% align:start
[Weather] This is just sad.

00:16:44.371 --> 00:16:47.542 position:7% line:83% align:start
The kind of evil that doesn't
even realize it's evil...

00:16:47.575 --> 00:16:49.777 position:10% line:83% align:start
is the most disgusting kind
of them all!

00:16:50.678 --> 00:16:51.613 position:13% line:89% align:start
[Father Pucchi] Nineteen.

00:16:51.646 --> 00:16:53.046 position:10% line:89% align:start
[Anastasia] Pucchi's afraid.

00:16:53.080 --> 00:16:55.482 position:7% line:89% align:start
His expression... there's fear

00:16:55.517 --> 00:16:57.819 position:21% line:83% align:start
and despair written
all over his face!

00:16:57.852 --> 00:16:59.086 position:7% line:89% align:start
[Father Pucchi] Twenty-three.

00:16:59.119 --> 00:17:01.321 position:16% line:89% align:start
No. Stop this, Weather.

00:17:01.355 --> 00:17:03.758 position:10% line:89% align:start
You are the one who's wrong!

00:17:03.791 --> 00:17:04.759 position:5% line:89% align:start
You're the cursed one, brother!

00:17:04.792 --> 00:17:06.193 position:35% line:89% align:start
[screams]

00:17:06.226 --> 00:17:08.328 position:5% line:83% align:start
I'm the man that kept you alive
and this is how you repay...

00:17:08.362 --> 00:17:08.930 position:35% line:89% align:start
It's over!

00:17:08.963 --> 00:17:10.297 position:33% line:89% align:start
Die, Pucchi!

00:17:11.766 --> 00:17:12.667 position:19% line:89% align:start
[Father Pucchi grunts]

00:17:12.700 --> 00:17:13.500 position:27% line:89% align:start
[tires screech]

00:17:16.604 --> 00:17:18.540 position:19% line:83% align:start
[Ermes] What the hell
are you doing?

00:17:18.573 --> 00:17:19.541 position:21% line:89% align:start
I thought I told you

00:17:19.574 --> 00:17:21.676 position:5% line:83% align:start
that if you try anything weird,
I'd kill you!

00:17:21.709 --> 00:17:24.012 position:21% line:83% align:start
No, wait. There was
a sudden cloud of dust,

00:17:24.044 --> 00:17:25.445 position:19% line:83% align:start
and then, a stray nail
or something

00:17:25.479 --> 00:17:26.814 position:27% line:83% align:start
stabbed straight
through the tire.

00:17:26.848 --> 00:17:29.049 position:24% line:83% align:start
It isn't my fault
I lost control!

00:17:29.082 --> 00:17:30.718 position:21% line:89% align:start
Shut up, he's close.

00:17:30.752 --> 00:17:32.286 position:10% line:89% align:start
Weather is somewhere nearby.

00:17:32.319 --> 00:17:33.922 position:27% line:83% align:start
-The priest too!
-[driver grunts]

00:17:33.955 --> 00:17:36.658 position:35% line:83% align:start
Although,
something looks off outside.

00:17:36.691 --> 00:17:38.526 position:38% line:83% align:start
[grunts]
You're right.

00:17:38.560 --> 00:17:40.227 position:19% line:89% align:start
I can't see very well,

00:17:40.260 --> 00:17:42.095 position:7% line:83% align:start
but there's something strange
covering up the road.

00:17:42.129 --> 00:17:43.998 position:24% line:83% align:start
-[glass shatters]
-[Jolyne] Weather!

00:17:44.032 --> 00:17:47.669 position:16% line:83% align:start
I know you're close by.
Respond to me, Weather!

00:17:50.304 --> 00:17:52.040 position:13% line:89% align:start
What is going on out here?

00:17:52.072 --> 00:17:54.474 position:24% line:83% align:start
What kind of crazy
horror scene is this?

00:17:54.509 --> 00:17:57.077 position:5% line:83% align:start
[Jolyne] I can sense the priest
moving around nearby.

00:17:57.612 --> 00:17:59.379 position:24% line:89% align:start
He's super close.

00:17:59.413 --> 00:18:02.482 position:10% line:83% align:start
I need to find Weather fast
before it's too late.

00:18:02.517 --> 00:18:05.485 position:5% line:83% align:start
I have a feeling that something
terrible is happening.

00:18:05.520 --> 00:18:07.021 position:21% line:83% align:start
[Ermes] Is this wind
being stirred up

00:18:07.055 --> 00:18:08.288 position:19% line:89% align:start
by Weather's ability?

00:18:08.322 --> 00:18:10.792 position:21% line:83% align:start
Has that damn priest
not turned into a snail yet?

00:18:10.825 --> 00:18:12.492 position:16% line:89% align:start
I honestly have no idea.

00:18:12.527 --> 00:18:14.062 position:10% line:83% align:start
-I only know that he's here.
-[shudders]

00:18:14.094 --> 00:18:15.495 position:27% line:89% align:start
Let's find him!

00:18:15.530 --> 00:18:17.397 position:30% line:89% align:start
[somber music]

00:18:19.433 --> 00:18:20.233 position:35% line:89% align:start
[exclaims]

00:18:20.267 --> 00:18:22.302 position:10% line:89% align:start
Jolyne, I just saw someone.

00:18:22.336 --> 00:18:24.171 position:24% line:83% align:start
-He's over there!
-[gasps]

00:18:24.204 --> 00:18:25.773 position:21% line:83% align:start
[Ermes] I don't know
if it's Weather or the priest,

00:18:25.807 --> 00:18:27.675 position:7% line:89% align:start
but they're in that direction!

00:18:27.709 --> 00:18:31.012 position:24% line:83% align:start
Jolyne, the wind's
starting to disperse.

00:18:31.045 --> 00:18:33.648 position:16% line:83% align:start
Also, my body's turning
back to normal.

00:18:35.282 --> 00:18:36.751 position:24% line:89% align:start
Does this mean...

00:18:36.784 --> 00:18:38.653 position:33% line:89% align:start
[wind gusts]

00:18:41.455 --> 00:18:42.389 position:33% line:89% align:start
[both gasp]

00:18:42.422 --> 00:18:44.291 position:38% line:89% align:start
Pucchi!

00:18:45.292 --> 00:18:47.929 position:27% line:83% align:start
Hold on, Jolyne.
Our bodies and Stands

00:18:47.962 --> 00:18:48.830 position:16% line:83% align:start
still haven't recovered
all the way

00:18:48.863 --> 00:18:50.598 position:5% line:89% align:start
from transitioning into snails.

00:18:50.632 --> 00:18:53.768 position:10% line:83% align:start
We can't beat the priest now
in terms of power and speed.

00:18:53.801 --> 00:18:55.135 position:7% line:89% align:start
We have to find Weather first.

00:18:55.168 --> 00:18:57.872 position:10% line:83% align:start
Well, if we beat the priest,
we can find Weather too!

00:18:57.905 --> 00:18:59.439 position:30% line:83% align:start
-Stone Ocean!
-[crackles]

00:18:59.473 --> 00:19:01.208 position:35% line:89% align:start
[whooshes]

00:19:01.241 --> 00:19:03.276 position:24% line:83% align:start
-[tires screeches]
-[Ermes] Jolyne!

00:19:03.310 --> 00:19:05.312 position:35% line:83% align:start
-[screams]
-[rope whooshing]

00:19:08.650 --> 00:19:09.550 position:30% line:89% align:start
[Jolyne gasps]

00:19:09.584 --> 00:19:10.952 position:35% line:89% align:start
[screams]

00:19:10.985 --> 00:19:13.621 position:35% line:83% align:start
-What the?
-Weather!

00:19:13.655 --> 00:19:16.724 position:24% line:83% align:start
Nobody is capable
of catching up to me anymore.

00:19:16.758 --> 00:19:19.060 position:10% line:83% align:start
I suggest you enjoy the rest
of the days you have left

00:19:19.093 --> 00:19:21.228 position:27% line:83% align:start
with your family
and loved ones.

00:19:21.261 --> 00:19:23.798 position:21% line:83% align:start
Coming after me now
is utterly useless.

00:19:23.831 --> 00:19:26.000 position:30% line:89% align:start
I always win.

00:19:26.034 --> 00:19:28.002 position:24% line:83% align:start
-[grunts, screams]
-[snail slime sputters]

00:19:28.036 --> 00:19:29.403 position:33% line:83% align:start
[Anastasia]
Don't do it, Jolyne!

00:19:29.737 --> 00:19:30.571 position:38% line:89% align:start
[groans]

00:19:31.371 --> 00:19:33.041 position:21% line:89% align:start
[Jolyne] Anastasia!

00:19:33.074 --> 00:19:35.242 position:19% line:83% align:start
This man is no longer
the priest.

00:19:35.275 --> 00:19:37.945 position:10% line:83% align:start
Who we know as Father Pucchi
isn't here anymore.

00:19:37.979 --> 00:19:38.846 position:41% line:89% align:start
What?

00:19:41.149 --> 00:19:43.751 position:19% line:83% align:start
-This is a revelation.
-[gasps]

00:19:43.785 --> 00:19:47.055 position:19% line:83% align:start
That's not him either.
It's one of his abilities.

00:19:47.088 --> 00:19:49.057 position:16% line:89% align:start
He made an after-image.

00:19:49.090 --> 00:19:50.725 position:35% line:89% align:start
[buzzing]

00:19:50.758 --> 00:19:52.259 position:27% line:89% align:start
[Jolyne] Versus!

00:19:52.292 --> 00:19:54.028 position:10% line:83% align:start
[Anastasia] Using the cover
of the wind,

00:19:54.062 --> 00:19:55.495 position:24% line:83% align:start
the priest planted
a past memory

00:19:55.530 --> 00:19:57.098 position:13% line:89% align:start
into this poor guy's head.

00:19:57.131 --> 00:19:58.432 position:35% line:89% align:start
[whirring]

00:19:58.465 --> 00:20:01.536 position:16% line:83% align:start
He used his own ability
to craft an image of himself.

00:20:01.569 --> 00:20:05.106 position:7% line:83% align:start
The presence you were feeling
earlier was Versus.

00:20:05.139 --> 00:20:07.441 position:16% line:83% align:start
Pucchi took this chance
to execute him.

00:20:09.443 --> 00:20:11.746 position:27% line:83% align:start
[Father Pucchi]
This is a revelation.

00:20:11.779 --> 00:20:14.015 position:5% line:83% align:start
It would seem there's something
on my side

00:20:14.048 --> 00:20:15.950 position:33% line:83% align:start
that can be
only classified as fate...

00:20:15.983 --> 00:20:17.217 position:21% line:83% align:start
The threads of fate
are aiding me

00:20:17.250 --> 00:20:18.786 position:24% line:83% align:start
in reaching heaven
in three days

00:20:18.820 --> 00:20:19.821 position:21% line:89% align:start
during the new moon.

00:20:19.854 --> 00:20:21.321 position:10% line:89% align:start
If it were not for destiny,

00:20:21.354 --> 00:20:22.924 position:24% line:83% align:start
I would've surely
been defeated...

00:20:22.957 --> 00:20:24.559 position:13% line:89% align:start
Do you believe in gravity?

00:20:24.592 --> 00:20:27.762 position:10% line:83% align:start
That is the reason why every
one of you came here today.

00:20:28.996 --> 00:20:29.597 position:38% line:89% align:start
Weather!

00:20:29.931 --> 00:20:31.165 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:20:31.199 --> 00:20:33.266 position:13% line:89% align:start
I told you, it's not him.

00:20:33.300 --> 00:20:35.636 position:16% line:83% align:start
-No one can pursue me...
-...can pursue me...

00:20:35.670 --> 00:20:37.872 position:24% line:83% align:start
...can pursue me!
[voice fades]

00:20:37.905 --> 00:20:39.207 position:35% line:89% align:start
[gurgling]

00:20:39.239 --> 00:20:41.008 position:35% line:89% align:start
[shudders]

00:20:41.042 --> 00:20:44.112 position:16% line:83% align:start
The snails are all gone.
This is...

00:20:44.145 --> 00:20:45.479 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Jolyne]
Where's Weather, Anastasia?

00:20:45.513 --> 00:20:46.346 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:20:46.379 --> 00:20:49.382 position:27% line:83% align:start
Where did he go?
Ermes, did you see him?

00:20:49.416 --> 00:20:52.053 position:27% line:83% align:start
Can you not feel
his presence anymore?

00:20:52.086 --> 00:20:53.386 position:35% line:89% align:start
[exclaims]

00:20:53.420 --> 00:20:55.322 position:10% line:83% align:start
[Ermes] You mean, you really
can't tell where he is?

00:20:57.592 --> 00:20:58.425 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:21:00.260 --> 00:21:00.995 position:38% line:89% align:start
Emporio!

00:21:01.662 --> 00:21:02.930 position:30% line:89% align:start
[tragic music]

00:21:07.201 --> 00:21:10.037 position:16% line:89% align:start
Hey, Ermes. He's there.

00:21:10.071 --> 00:21:11.506 position:30% line:83% align:start
Call a doctor.
He should've healed...

00:21:11.539 --> 00:21:12.907 position:38% line:83% align:start
-Jolyne.
-...from the snails by now!

00:21:12.940 --> 00:21:14.041 position:35% line:83% align:start
-Emporio!
-Jolyne!

00:21:14.075 --> 00:21:14.842 position:41% line:89% align:start
Uh...

00:21:16.911 --> 00:21:18.679 position:10% line:89% align:start
I'm sorry, the wind stopped.

00:21:24.652 --> 00:21:27.688 position:33% line:83% align:start
The rainbow
disappeared too, Jolyne.

00:21:34.595 --> 00:21:35.563 position:38% line:89% align:start
No way.

00:21:37.565 --> 00:21:41.202 position:7% line:83% align:start
[Jolyne] It can't be. Is this
because we crashed the car?

00:21:41.235 --> 00:21:42.970 position:27% line:83% align:start
Or is it because
I came after him?

00:21:43.638 --> 00:21:44.471 position:38% line:89% align:start
But why?

00:21:46.808 --> 00:21:48.676 position:27% line:89% align:start
Listen, Jolyne.

00:21:48.709 --> 00:21:51.478 position:5% line:83% align:start
Plenty of people have called me
a murderer.

00:21:51.512 --> 00:21:54.248 position:16% line:83% align:start
At least that's what the
newspapers said about me.

00:21:54.282 --> 00:21:56.416 position:33% line:83% align:start
And I don't
necessarily disagree.

00:21:57.752 --> 00:22:00.922 position:5% line:83% align:start
When people asked me if I would
sacrifice myself for my family,

00:22:01.923 --> 00:22:04.258 position:21% line:89% align:start
I told them all, no.

00:22:04.292 --> 00:22:07.261 position:16% line:83% align:start
I don't think my answer
would change even now.

00:22:07.295 --> 00:22:10.898 position:7% line:83% align:start
When it came to my parents, my
heart was never moved by them.

00:22:11.331 --> 00:22:13.201 position:35% line:89% align:start
However...

00:22:13.234 --> 00:22:14.902 position:19% line:83% align:start
I know I'd be willing
to risk my life

00:22:14.936 --> 00:22:17.071 position:13% line:83% align:start
for those that revived me
from the dead

00:22:17.104 --> 00:22:19.240 position:13% line:83% align:start
-without a second thought.
-[gasps]

00:22:19.273 --> 00:22:20.975 position:27% line:83% align:start
It was like that
for Weather, too.

00:22:25.947 --> 00:22:26.948 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:22:27.815 --> 00:22:28.683 position:21% line:89% align:start
[Emporio] That's...

00:22:30.417 --> 00:22:31.752 position:24% line:89% align:start
[Anastasia] Yeah.

00:22:31.786 --> 00:22:34.354 position:10% line:83% align:start
When Pale Snake was focused
on dealing the final blow,

00:22:34.387 --> 00:22:36.423 position:24% line:83% align:start
he took advantage
of his special ability.

00:22:37.592 --> 00:22:38.693 position:21% line:89% align:start
He used that moment

00:22:38.726 --> 00:22:40.695 position:21% line:83% align:start
to seal his ability
into a disc.

00:22:42.897 --> 00:22:43.531 position:16% line:89% align:start
[Emporio] Hey, Jolyne...

00:22:44.431 --> 00:22:46.601 position:27% line:83% align:start
I think Weather
entrusted this to you.

00:22:46.934 --> 00:22:47.802 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:22:52.340 --> 00:22:53.708 position:13% line:89% align:start
Weather came back to life

00:22:53.741 --> 00:22:56.143 position:16% line:83% align:start
when he finally escaped
from that prison.

00:22:56.177 --> 00:22:57.712 position:21% line:83% align:start
And that's the proof
he left for you.

00:23:00.748 --> 00:23:03.684 position:19% line:83% align:start
In his final few days,
he was happy.

00:23:04.652 --> 00:23:06.821 position:5% line:89% align:start
Weather had already been saved!

00:23:08.155 --> 00:23:09.090 position:35% line:89% align:start
[sniffles]

00:23:10.224 --> 00:23:10.925 position:35% line:89% align:start
Weather...

00:23:11.359 --> 00:23:13.828 position:41% line:89% align:start
[sobs]

00:23:16.330 --> 00:23:17.665 position:27% line:89% align:start
One more time...

00:23:17.698 --> 00:23:19.000 position:41% line:89% align:start
[sobs]

00:23:19.033 --> 00:23:22.703 position:19% line:83% align:start
I wanna speak with you
just one more time.

00:23:22.737 --> 00:23:24.071 position:35% line:89% align:start
[sniffles]

00:23:24.538 --> 00:23:26.173 position:27% line:89% align:start
Just once more,

00:23:26.207 --> 00:23:29.476 position:7% line:83% align:start
[sniffles] I wanna talk to you
in the soft breeze.

